title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 17 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 17 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Governor Bill Lee of Tennessee joined Clay and Buck to talk about letting parents decide whether kids wear masks. Vaccine passports will just divide people. Let states decide how to govern. For Democrats, their only enemies are domestic. C&B analyzes the spin coming from the administration press conference. How many Americans did Biden leave behind in Afghanistan?
